comments: Morris Sr. (PHI) establishes himself in Tate's (HOU) path and absorbs the incoming contact from Tate (HOU) during the pick.
Sengun (HOU) turns to roll towards the basket and incidental contact occurs with Beverley (PHI) as Beverley goes under the pick.
Morris Sr. (PHI) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Eason (HOU) does not place his hand underneath the ball during his dribble.
Maxey (PHI) reaches in and grazes Eason's (HOU) arm during his driving shot attempt, which is marginal.
Sengun (HOU) reaches in and brushes Maxey's (PHI) off-arm during his drive, which is marginal.
Maxey (PHI) gathers the ball as he's airborne and lands on both feet as he establishes his left foot as his pivot, which he maintains.
As Maxey's (PHI) is pivoting, he brushes Tate's (HOU) body, which does not dislodge him from his legally obtained position.
Eason (HOU) reaches in and deflects the ball during Harris' (PHI) attempt to pass.
Eason (HOU) makes slight contact to Melton's (PHI) arm as he rips-through at the start of the drive, which he is able to move through.
Eason (HOU) moves alongside Melton's (PHI) path and the body contact that occurs during the driving shot attempt is marginal.
Sengun (HOU) bobbles the incoming pass before legally recovering and starting his dribble.
Morris Sr. (PHI) avoids stepping out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
After Tate (HOU) makes clean contact to the ball he grazes Melton's (PHI) wrist while he's pivoting, which does not affect his control of the ball.
Sengun (HOU) makes contact with Maxey's (PHI) head that affects his driving shot attempt.
VanVleet (HOU) contests Morris Sr.'s (PHI) jump shot attempt and makes contact with his leg, which his affects his ability to return to the floor.
Tate (HOU) releases the inbounds pass within five seconds.
Melton (PHI) reaches in and cleanly deflects the ball during Green's (HOU) dribble.
Sengun (HOU) commits a take foul on Melton (PHI).
Melton (PHI) makes contact with Green's (HOU) body at the start of the drive, which he is able to move through.
Morris Sr. (PHI) has an extended forearm that makes contact with Green (HOU) and then removes during the driving shot attempt, which is marginal.
Green (HOU) initiates contact with Harris's (PHI) arm in the backcourt that affects his ability to gather.
Sengun (HOU) commits a take foul on Melton (PHI).
Maxey (PHI) absorbs the body contact with Landale (HOU) and Morris Sr. (PHI) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball.
Landale (HOU) commits a take foul on Morris Sr. (PHI).
